quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  106,1,"Khulwa omunalo kwa Abakuraish."
  106,2,"Okhunala khwabu tsinjendo tsieyirotso nende tsieshirumbi."
  106,3,"Khomana balaame Nyasaye Omulesi owe Inzu ino."
  106,4,"Ulia ubaliisinjia ninabelenje inzala, mana nabahelesia omulembe okhurulana nende oburi."
  107,1,"Koo! Olutsikhwo ulia ukananga omurungo kwa inyanga ya indukho?"
  107,2,"Ni ulia uluumanga (usindikhanga) Omwana omufwilwa."
  107,3,"Ne shakholangakhwo eshinani shokhulisia omutakha tawe."
  107,4,"Oooh, eshinyasio eshikhongo shili khubalia balaamanga."
  107,5,"Balia beyibilisinjia okhulaama khwabu."
  107,6,"Balia belolosinjia."
  107,7,"Ne bekalilanga obukhonyi."
  108,1,"Toto khwakhuhelesia obulayi obunji."
  108,2,"Kho laama ne osinze khulwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi."
  108,3,"Toto ulia ukhusila niye ulakhalishilwa muno (olwibulo nende amakhuwa keke)."